1
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,400
Take me to the lighthouse.

2
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,040
I wanna see

3
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,680
what it's like.

4
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,159
But

5
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,400
it's far away.

6
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,359
But for you,

7
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,599
it only takes a few minutes.

8
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,000
What?

9
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,719
You're not telling me the truth,

10
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:25,879
are you?

11
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:39,640
Here we are.

12
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,760
It's beautiful.

13
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,319
By the way,

14
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,200
how did you get back to Black Rock Island?

15
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,640
The ability of the Wolf Clan

16
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,439
only awakens at adulthood.

17
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,319
Sixteen years ago,

18
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:57,560
I heard about villagers fighting wild wolves,

19
00:01:58,599 --> 00:01:59,319
so I came to the island

20
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,280
and saved Zhang San and Li Si.

21
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,400
Later, I found many descendants of the Wolf Clan

22
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:05,400
on this island,

23
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,280
and took them in.

24
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:10,599
It's indeed a good place to live in seclusion.

25
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,000
It's my duty to protect people around me,

26
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:19,879
including you.

27
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,159
Aren't you afraid I'm an undercover?

28
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,479
I trust you.

29
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,439
I was badly injured that day.

30
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:29,400
You could have done anything to me.

31
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,639
But you took care of me all night.

32
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,800
It feels good

33
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:38,919
not to be abandoned.

34
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,360
Actually,

35
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,759
I'm not as kind as you think.

36
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:48,800
I approached you

37
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:51,120
to use your identity as the Wolf King

38
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,759
to find out the murderer

39
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,919
who caused my mom and me to drown.

40
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:57,800
I even suspect

41
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,400
that the murderer

42
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,680
is you.

43
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,479
Sixteen years ago,

44
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,960
I met a mother and daughter

45
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,039
near the port.

46
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,120
Mom,

47
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,560
are there really wolves here?

48
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,159
We've been here for so long,

49
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,360
we haven't seen one.

50
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,439
Wolves?

51
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,960
I really haven't seen any.

52
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,199
But I did see

53
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,479
a whale.

54
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,319
Mom,

55
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,240
can we go see the whale?

56
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,719
Eat first.

57
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:48,879
Later,

58
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,360
I heard someone calling for help.

59
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,719
Mom!

60
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,960
Mom, help me!

61
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,520
Mom.

62
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,159
Help me.

63
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:20,879
Are you still cold?

64
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,480
It turns out

65
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:26,160
you saved me 16 years ago.

66
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,040
Qin Yeren has been doing evil for years.

67
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:31,759
He probably

68
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,639
deliberately tricked you into the sea

69
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,360
to kill you for money.

70
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,199
I will find his evidence of crimes.

71
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,160
I'll go with you.

72
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,319
We'll work together

73
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,600
to bring him to justice.

74
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:50,879
But

75
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,920
before that,

76
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,480
you have to stay by my side.

77
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,279
Why?

78
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,920
Now everyone is saying

79
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,199
that you are Lu Zhiyu's woman.

80
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,680
And someone is offering a high price

81
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:04,000
for your life.

82
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,560
So you have to stay by my side.

83
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,519
You can't go anywhere.

84
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,439
And your brother

85
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,160
doesn't seem like a good guy.

86
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,160
Do you want it medium-rare or...

87
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:36,920
You...

88
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,240
Sorry,

89
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:47,560
I forgot you're afraid of fire.

90
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,399
What else are you afraid of?

91
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,279
I'll write it all down.

92
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,040
Just a few dietary restrictions,

93
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:57,759
like

94
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,839
alcohol,

95
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,360
caffeine,

96
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,079
theobromine,

97
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,120
And...

98
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,160
And milk.

99
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,839
These are all not allowed.

100
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,439
Just like my Duoduo.

101
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,120
Who is Duoduo?

102
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:22,000
A golden retriever I used to have.

103
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,839
It was this tall when standing up.

104
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,399
It even helped me pick up deliveries.

105
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:30,120
My clothes have arrived.

106
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,720
Thank you, Lu Duoduo.

107
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:37,879
Your delivery.

108
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,399
Lu Duoduo,

109
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,439
Which one

110
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,560
looks better on me?

111
00:06:59,160 --> 00:06:59,680
Lu Duoduo.

112
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,319
Both are fine.

113
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,839
Do you have a crush on your master?

114
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,759
Zang Feng Guard.

115
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,560
I was underage when I joined Zang Feng.

116
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,360
Don't talk nonsense.

117
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,759
Okay, I got it.

118
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,639
It's daylight.

119
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,279
Don't you need to go back to sleep?

120
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,079
I need to adjust my routine

121
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,360
to adapt to your life rhythm.

122
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:40,959
Why?

123
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,639
I'm afraid that you might play tricks

124
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,959
and escape from me

125
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,040
to tell your brother

126
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,279
about the secret.

127
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,560
You don't even trust me.

128
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:56,079
I'll tell him

129
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,360
right now.

130
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,120
Hello, Moon.

131
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:03,639
What's your plan for today?

132
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:07,360
Sunbathing on the beach,

133
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,160
and then shopping and eating.

134
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,240
I'm free today.

135
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,120
Let's go together.

136
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,199
Okay.

137
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,800
Brother

138
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:20,000
The local guide I hired

139
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,519
is not qualified at all.

140
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,120
I haven't even had a good time

141
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,399
since I came here.

142
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,519
What a surprise.

143
00:08:34,639 --> 00:08:35,600
As a bodyguard,

144
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,279
I should protect my boss

145
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,840
of my employer.

146
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:44,039
Does the bodyguard eat together?

147
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:45,919
Brother.

148
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:48,120
Because he is more...

149
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,200
Because Miss Jiang promised my job

150
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,399
includes meals and accommodation.

151
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,000
Right.

152
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,799
He is more responsible.

153
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,240
Truffle salad.

154
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,159
French baked blue lobster.

155
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,919
Spanish seafood rice.

156
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:09,600
Wine is Château Lafite Rothschild.

157
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,360
I want a caramel sea salt ice cream.

158
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,039
Thank you.

159
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,279
Are you full with these?

160
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:15,519
Lu Zhiyu,

161
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:16,759
why don't you order more?

162
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,840
My brother is treating.

163
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,399
M9 Australian beef steak.

164
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:23,480
Three.

165
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,159
What level of doneness do you want?

166
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,879
Two medium well,

167
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:27,799
one

168
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,720
raw.

169
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,039
The dietary habits of the indigenous people

170
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,639
are indeed barbaric.

171
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,240
You treat different people differently.

172
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,120
This gentleman

173
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,600
also needs service.

174
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:51,399
No need.

175
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,200
He knows I don't drink.

176
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,519
Mr. Lu is the boss of the business circle.

177
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,639
Right, I almost forgot.

178
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,399
The entire business circle is his.

179
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,320
All your expenses today

180
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,200
are on the house.

181
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,039
Go ahead.

182
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,559
What?

183
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,399
My brother went to talk about business.

184
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,159
Are you sure you don't want to follow him?

185
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,840
The driver who drives him

186
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,759
is also my man.

187
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,360
You're so cunning.

188
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,480
Why are you telling me now?

189
00:10:37,919 --> 00:10:38,960
You're not afraid I'll tell someone?

190
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,000
I believe

191
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,519
you also want to know

192
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,720
if your brother is innocent.

193
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,200
If he really

194
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,000
colludes with Qin Yeren

195
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:49,240
to hurt my people,

196
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,799
I won't let him go.

197
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,240
What if you misunderstand him?

198
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,799
If I misunderstand him,

199
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:57,039
I'll invite him to dinner again.

200
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,440
So,

201
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,240
are you shopping with me now?

202
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,159
Yes.

203
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:08,679
I want to go

204
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:10,679
there.

205
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,279
A bit more to the right.

206
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:14,279
This one.

207
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,159
Grab the one behind.

208
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,080
Okay, right.

209
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:17,360
Put it down.

210
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:25,879
I'll do it myself.

211
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,320
Go away.

212
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,080
This one.

213
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,679
This one.

214
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,399
Right.

215
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:31,120
Right.

216
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,159
Go away.

217
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,240
You'll break it.

218
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,480
You've fixed these machines.

219
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,519
You're cheating us.

220
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,200
Take whatever you want.

221
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,480
It's boring.

222
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:00,000
What should I call it?

223
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:03,360
How about Lu Duoduo?

224
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,519
Lu Duoduo.

225
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,120
Beauty,

226
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,039
this is the girl

227
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,200
who can drink a lot.

228
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,720
Have a few more drinks with me.

229
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:10,720
Have a drink.

230
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:11,919
We met in a bar.

231
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,360
You wore the ancient dress.

232
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,399
Isn't this your subordinate?

233
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,200
Really?

234
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,279
You must have the wrong person. What are you talking about?

235
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:19,879
Shut up.

236
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:21,039
You treat her as a goddess,

237
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,840
but she treats you as a lackey.

238
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:37,840
Lu Duoduo,

239
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,480
from now on,

240
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,200
I'm your master.

241
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:45,960
Miss Jiang,

242
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:50,240
is this another delivery for you?

243
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:51,919
What's this?

244
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,440
Could you help me open it and take a look?

245
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:57,320
Old Wang.

246
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,279
There's also a card.

247
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,399
Shop owner's message.

248
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:15,759
Wish you a long-lasting love,

249
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,679
a century of harmony.

250
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,519
This is good.

251
00:13:32,919 --> 00:13:33,639
Hurry up.

252
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,000
It should be

253
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:44,879
a thousand years of happiness.

254
00:13:49,039 --> 00:13:49,600
Be careful.

255
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:00,360
Wait for me.

256
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:11,240
Aren't you just gonna lick it?

257
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,679
Why do you need this?

258
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,080
I just bought it.

259
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:25,519
But my wound heals slowly.

260
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,960
You're too obvious.

261
00:14:30,519 --> 00:14:31,039
No.

262
00:14:32,399 --> 00:14:33,279
You're not happy

263
00:14:33,519 --> 00:14:35,879
because the brand can't

264
00:14:36,759 --> 00:14:37,639
order me anymore, right?

265
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:42,679
Did I hurt you?

266
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,320
What would you do

267
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:47,720
if I said yes?

268
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,559
Then it's no.

269
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,279
Do you want me to keep licking you?

270
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:54,840
Dream on.

271
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:01,120
I know

272
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,799
the brand disappeared

273
00:15:05,679 --> 00:15:07,519
because you thought

274
00:15:08,279 --> 00:15:09,840
I was your master, Li Feiyuan,

275
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,399
so you obeyed me without question.

276
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,799
Now that the truth is out,

277
00:15:17,639 --> 00:15:18,879
I'm just an ordinary person.

278
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,759
So the master-servant relationship

279
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,360
no longer exists.

280
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:25,720
Right?

281
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:30,200
Maybe.

282
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:35,320
Truth revealed, case solved, yay!

283
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:39,720
Thank you.
